Use the `@tracked` decorator from `@glimmer/tracking` before a class field to make it reactive. When `playerName` changes, the template automatically re-renders. Always initialize string properties with a default string value to avoid undefined rendering issues.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
import { tracked } from '@glimmer/tracking';

export default class ScoreDisplayComponent extends Component {
  @tracked runs = 0;

  <template>
    <span class="text-2xl font-bold">{{this.runs}}</span>
  </template>
