```
Declare a `@tracked` number property just like a string — prefix the class field with the `@tracked` decorator. Initializing to `0` ensures the template always renders a valid number. Any assignment like `this.runs = 45` will trigger a re-render.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
import { tracked } from '@glimmer/tracking';

export default class InningsStatusComponent extends Component {
  @tracked isInningsComplete = false;

  <template>
    {{#if this.isInningsComplete}}
